{"tid":480220,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【超長期年金】400元供60年 退休月袋2萬元 年金識變魔法？","createTime":"2017-11-26T02:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T16:00:45.000Z","uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"df01e03e6a9aa47ad0ce7e8d5f5579af011945d2","tid":480220,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"按揭證券公司擬明年推公共年金，針對65歲後銀髮一族，至於本港私營年金市場，則主攻後生世代，起始供款日更可於出生日起計，即意味家長可於0歲起幫兒女供款，而複式效應相當誇張，每月供400元，退休後可獲得1.85萬元的效果。<br />\n<br />\n以最近推出的中銀人壽年金為例，其供款期最長可達60年，若果以最低月供金額400元計，供足60年，總供款金額將達28.8萬元，而65歲後，每月收取年金則為1.85萬元，若果長壽至90歲，總獲得年金則達554.2萬元。<br />\n若果選擇另一種供款方式，以美國萬通年金為例，即僅於出生後首5年供款，每月供款金額較大，約為1,200元，總供款金額為7.2萬元，然後供款人可以等待60年後，隨着資金逐漸滾大，65歲後的每月年金高達1.86萬元；而若果以相等供款額，不止供5年，而是供足10年，65歲後每月年金更可達3.1萬元。<br />\n不過，投資這類超長期年金前，實際需要考慮眾多因素：<br />\n1.預期回報未必達標<br />\n年金實際是一項投資工具，當保險公司接受供款後，即會開展投資，例如定息工具或股票，並在退休後逐漸將投資所得發回予投資者，但須注意回報有分保證、非保證兩類，意味最終獲得年金可大可小。以中銀人壽為例，該公司預期回報率為4.9%，保證回報率則為2%至3%。<br />\n2.通脹是最大敵人<br />\n以0歲開始供，每月供400元，供足60年計，在65歲退休後，將可以收取每月1.85萬元年金，但值得注意的是，假設65年間通脹率為2.5%，該筆每月年金的現值（present value）為約3,716元。不過供款金額亦因為通脹上升而減少，按上述通脹率計，65年後400元現值等於現在80元。<br />\n3.承受保險機構倒閉風險<br />\n若果參與人由零歲開始幫兒子供年金，兒子並於65歲提取，若果屆時該兒子於100歲終老，意味整個參與期長達100年，故此參與人宜選擇財政實力強橫，並有信心可以陪伴逾100年的機構，不過以AIG為例，其於1919年成立，但在2008年幾乎倒閉。<br />\n4.年金對沖長壽風險<br />\n年金與一般儲蓄保險最大差異，在於前者是對沖年齡過長風險，因為目前不少年金是保障受益人終身甚至是100歲，而若果人均年齡愈長，對於保險公司的承保風險愈大，而若果受益人不幸較早逝世，保險公司通常會扣保費後發還供款，實際有如「白供」。<br />\n記者：周家誠<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171125/large/1511616585_93c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171125%2Flarge%2F1511616585_93c6.jpg&h=1b2f9125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171126/large/1511627229_f2c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171126%2Flarge%2F1511627229_f2c0.jpg&h=b31b5909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171126/large/1511627243_b1c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171126%2Flarge%2F1511627243_b1c3.jpg&h=a4e7bbfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171126/57505160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171126%2F57505160&d=r%2F49uCi42EMBuif2e4VsKG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=607dc9dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171126%2F57505160&h=259ac534\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171126/57505160</a>"},{"pid":"304046491a562b2c9fadca72b15e32d53485d6d2","tid":480220,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"最小供千二，實際供萬二"},{"pid":"f8ebca9b82414b92739f347e4b4d3c77bac6d7c0","tid":480220,"uid":4896,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"60年後嘅錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一年3.5%通漲<br />\n60年後都近8倍物價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d535f5234e6fe8bfb1cdd941cd9beda51b7b7766","tid":480220,"uid":4896,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:14:33.000Z","msg":"仲要<span style=\"color: red;\">月</span>供變<span style=\"color: red;\">年</span>金呢d字眼fake on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9c6f75ff236e964543cf57ed9403a4fb624038","tid":480220,"uid":27591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:22:48.000Z","msg":"唔可以忘記通漲"},{"pid":"a1fc25712b6cced0c78f55da9be31b9e93d29269","tid":480220,"uid":44454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:27:25.000Z","msg":"等如1957開始供400元，你依家就有2萬元一個月了，如果將400元供樓或買股票，你估差幾遠？"},{"pid":"489cb44e57770842272b119b27f44db687941d3b","tid":480220,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等如1957開始供400元，你依家就有2萬元一個月了，如果將400元供樓或買股票，你估差幾遠？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n禁睇下你買邊隻既姐，好多汁左"},{"pid":"dd56d8f434d1c7b4b10eee357d2a2fe2feddaf8b","tid":480220,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:12:45.000Z","msg":"呢d垃圾年金真係害人不淺，根本係保險公司為呃水，所有條款著數完全偏向保險公司"},{"pid":"6058d8be7243c3bf5c0f917f9def6b00de37454d","tid":480220,"uid":21634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾年金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c78e5112c3883b3985549e390876d848f19e52","tid":480220,"uid":68993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"保險供60年係咩玩法"},{"pid":"3158eccd96fa1d6c4bccd624ab192732ecbd5daf","tid":480220,"uid":14867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T04:54:59.000Z","msg":"遲啲政府出lump sum annuity <br />\n唔想比保險公司賺可以留意下"},{"pid":"2e785741811dafecf020c1aa367a2a9ace7b192e","tid":480220,"uid":6889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等如1957開始供400元，你依家就有2萬元一個月了，如果將400元供樓或買股票，你估差幾遠？</blockquote><br />\n1957年$400買到咩，同今日$20000買到咩就大概知無so 喇！"},{"pid":"c33e131b6e039082391efef79b804eee9f7ddce2","tid":480220,"uid":83709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"adc8aa77a293da63c41248bea3e2e210fdc17bf6","tid":480220,"uid":14867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:08:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每月年金果個數係咪姐係要除番12個月?</blockquote><br />\n唔使，年金只係產品嘅名，最初每年咁比，後來發展到每月/每年咁比都有"},{"pid":"384b0a1e556ac384632117f8d4c90be1e3a1b42a","tid":480220,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:11:06.000Z","msg":"一定仲有 60 年命咩，不如話供 150 年有 10 萬每個月"},{"pid":"d22778e0463d8a47dda4c1ea895c68afa44042fb","tid":480220,"uid":8511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:13:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定仲有 60 年命咩，不如話供 150 年有 10 萬每個月</blockquote><br />\n最好無risk 就俾錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5889c6f8277b22944c8af2f9f4c39867274337","tid":480220,"uid":30841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T05:29:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定仲有 60 年命咩，不如話供 150 年有 10 萬每個月</blockquote><br />\n最好無risk 就俾錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講好似你有份分咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十年後咩世界都唔知"},{"pid":"605cd2b4d5ef920a6df057beb8e3680e17226640","tid":480220,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遲啲政府出lump sum annuity <br />\n唔想比保險公司賺可以留意下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n懷疑政府都係搵保險公司託<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1568f6ff036ef74bb7eff830a557bc8c91373ab","tid":480220,"uid":65139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:43:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定仲有 60 年命咩，不如話供 150 年有 10 萬每個月</blockquote><br />\n最好無risk 就俾錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講好似你有份分咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十年後咩世界都唔知</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRisk premium係投資知識黎<br />\n唔好係咪都笑人先"},{"pid":"6a4ce1a4b0440be02e28ab57328dd6e8d80e3ac3","tid":480220,"uid":8511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定仲有 60 年命咩，不如話供 150 年有 10 萬每個月</blockquote><br />\n最好無risk 就俾錢你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你咁講好似你有份分咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十年後咩世界都唔知</blockquote><br />\n無話叫你買定唔買<br />\n佢就係博你唔知十年廿年後咩世界先隨年期越長越高回報姐<br />\n正如佢知十年後蝕硬, 佢唔會開<br />\n你知你賺硬, 必買"},{"pid":"efda4a4ddb4edc35850793ef66cd7acfd830257d","tid":480220,"uid":65139,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"如果懶計可以參考下下面 IRR (扣鳩通漲之後):<br />\n<br />\n假設你90歲未釘, 保險公司冇收皮, 張圖吹個return係保證... <br />\n當黎緊幾十年平均通漲都係2%左右<br />\n由上至下:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171126/large/1511627229_f2c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171126%2Flarge%2F1511627229_f2c0.jpg&h=b31b5909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIRR          扣鳩通漲(-2%)<br />\n5.78%\t3.78%<br />\n5.75%\t3.75%<br />\n5.77%\t3.77%<br />\n5.79%\t3.79%<br />\n5.66%\t3.66%<br />\n5.61%\t3.61%<br />\n5.63%\t3.63%<br />\n5.44%\t3.44%<br />\n5.33%\t3.33%<br />\n5.27%\t3.27%<br />\n5.20%\t3.20%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171126/large/1511627243_b1c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171126%2Flarge%2F1511627243_b1c3.jpg&h=a4e7bbfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIRR          扣鳩通漲(-2%)<br />\n6.18%\t4.18%<br />\n6.12%\t4.12%<br />\n6.06%\t4.06%<br />\n6.00%\t4.00%<br />\n5.74%\t3.74%<br />\n5.68%\t3.68%<br />\n<br />\n然後再參考下美帝30年risk free bond<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/183238_6a6b57fa48ba900b1a99c7cfec3b5956.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F183238_6a6b57fa48ba900b1a99c7cfec3b5956.JPG&h=bdafcbc8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4389e115efd30fae516a28315752bf4230177a23","tid":480220,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:00:22.000Z","msg":"萬通個個好似幾好<br />\n有冇高人評論下"},{"pid":"8f778d32ea6fe52202f70a9987175657784a2fb5","tid":480220,"uid":29608,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"同連登仔講投資就算9數，想人地幫佢賺錢，就一蚊都唔想比人賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a2c9db247be74b1d0ef6386b060e6c4d86a267","tid":480220,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:25:43.000Z","msg":"不如睇下1980S 90S 2000<br />\n樓價同麥記價錢"},{"pid":"244baf0d004e50870e822f5621a34fed9ed52065","tid":480220,"uid":139314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T11:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同連登仔講投資就算9數，想人地幫佢賺錢，就一蚊都唔想比人賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢樣真<br />\n連登仔不勞而獲最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}